{"tid":2488192,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"12. 19  黃 店 感 謝 日","createTime":"2021-04-14T05:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T09:18:12.000Z","uid":357031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb132cef706ddec1e0deba25a04fae7cbaa3134","tid":2488192,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"12月19日請盡香港公民責任，全城排隊支持黃店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打請推posts <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年12月19日不如搞個黃店感謝日,一齊排隊爆買黃店..全城排黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487014\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n19/12攪黃店感謝日, 唔得閒去投票, 無人犯法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487027\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487027</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n投票日叫人去黃店排隊，條龍長撚過票站，畫面好似幾好睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487632\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n12月19日係我最喜愛黃店選舉日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2487624\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2487624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"135f9ebd25d1b8c0ae11bce84736aed0dbde70da","tid":2488192,"uid":47658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"全民黑衫日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85420dbcadf587ea0443952a3673ef03aae57302","tid":2488192,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95d5c2edfec1b31e6e1549d805395297ff585d2","tid":2488192,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img s